The paper proposes an ensemble method for image classification using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of multiple models and strategies to increase diversity suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions partitioning input samples based on decision confidence scores, which could be related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE).
